Martin v. Platt et al. (Supreme Court, General Term, First Department. January 10, 1890.)

Argued before Van Brunt, P. J., and Brady and Daniels, JJ.

No opinion. Upon appellant’s stipulating to argue at the February Term, this motion will be denied. For former reports, see 4 N. Y. Supp. 359 ; 5 N. Y. Supp. 862; 7 N. Y. Supp. 950.
